quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,107,"Wa-in yamsaska Allahu bidurrinfala kashifa lahu illa huwa wa-in yuridkabikhayrin fala radda lifadlihi yuseebubihi man yashao min AAibadihi wahuwa alghafooru arraheem"
  10,108,"Qul ya ayyuha annasuqad jaakumu alhaqqu min rabbikum famani ihtadafa-innama yahtadee linafsihi waman dalla fa-innamayadillu AAalayha wama ana AAalaykumbiwakeel"
  10,109,"WattabiAA ma yoohailayka wasbir hatta yahkumaAllahu wahuwa khayru alhakimeen"
  11,1,"Alif-lam-ra kitabun ohkimatayatuhu thumma fussilat min ladun hakeeminkhabeer"
  11,2,"Alla taAAbudoo illa Allahainnanee lakum minhu natheerun wabasheer"
  11,3,"Waani istaghfiroo rabbakum thumma toobooilayhi yumattiAAkum mataAAan hasanan ilaajalin musamman wayu/ti kulla thee fadlin fadlahuwa-in tawallaw fa-inee akhafu AAalaykum AAathabayawmin kabeer"
  11,4,"Ila Allahi marjiAAukum wahuwaAAala kulli shay-in qadeer"
  11,5,"Ala innahum yathnoona sudoorahumliyastakhfoo minhu ala heena yastaghshoona thiyabahumyaAAlamu ma yusirroona wama yuAAlinoona innahuAAaleemun bithati assudoor"
